---
---
<section class="section reviews-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="reviews-header">
      <div class="reviews-summary">
        <h2>Customer Reviews</h2>
        <div class="rating-big">
          <span class="number">4.82</span>
          <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p>Based on 482 reviews</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rating-bars">
        <div class="bar-row">
          <span>5 Star</span>
          <div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 85%;"></div></div>
          <span>85%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bar-row">
          <span>4 Star</span>
          <div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 10%;"></div></div>
          <span>10%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bar-row">
          <span>3 Star</span>
          <div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 3%;"></div></div>
          <span>3%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bar-row">
          <span>2 Star</span>
          <div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 1%;"></div></div>
          <span>1%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bar-row">
          <span>1 Star</span>
          <div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 1%;"></div></div>
          <span>1%</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="reviews-list">
      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-meta">
          <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          <span class="date">Oct 12, 2023</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Best chameleon effect I've used</h3>
        <p>"The color shift is insane! I used this on my bike frame and the way it transitions from blue to purple in the sun is exactly what I was looking for. Very easy to apply without drips."</p>
        <span class="author"><strong>Alex M.</strong> - Verified Buyer</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-meta">
          <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          <span class="date">Sep 28, 2023</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Professional results</h3>
        <p>"I've used many brands for my custom models, but Spray Bazaar's gloss finish is on another level. It settles so smoothly. The nozzle they include for detail work is a game changer."</p>
        <span class="author"><strong>Sarah K.</strong> - Verified Buyer</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="reviews-footer">
      <button class="btn btn-outline">Read All Reviews</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .reviews-section {
    background: white;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }
  .reviews-header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .rating-big {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .rating-big .number {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    display: block;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .rating-big .stars {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }
  
  .rating-bars {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .bar-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr 40px;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  .bar-bg {
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--bg-light);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: #ffb400;
  }
  
  .reviews-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .review-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }
  .review-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .review-meta .stars {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #ffb400;
  }
  .review-meta .date {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .review-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .review-card p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .author {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }
  
  .reviews-footer {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .reviews-header {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .reviews-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
